llm_outputs.rationale: The table on page 66 provides minimum dimensional requirements for different zoning districts. For the Mobile Home Overlay (R-15M) district, there are two values given for the minimum lot area, depending on whether public water or sewer is available.
llm_outputs.answer: 20,000 sq ft (if no public water or sewer); 15,000 sq ft (if public water or sewer)
